<div class="prose-content max-w-3xl">

  <h2>Compliments and suggestions</h2>
  <p>If you'd like to pass on thanks to a member of staff, or have a suggestion for how we could improve, please:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Speak to our reception team in person or by phone</li>
    <li>Email us at <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a></li>
    <li>Complete the NHS Friends and Family Test — ask at reception for a form</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Concerns and complaints</h2>
  <p>If something has gone wrong or you are unhappy with the care or service you've received, we'd like to know so we can put it right.</p>
  <p>In the first instance, please speak to our practice manager. You can:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Ask at reception to speak to the practice manager</li>
    <li>Write to us at Leven Health Centre, Victoria Road, Leven, Fife, KY8 4ET</li>
    <li>Email us at <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a> — please mark your email "Complaint"</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We will acknowledge your complaint within 3 working days and aim to respond fully within 20 working days.</p>

  <h2>Independent advice</h2>
  <p>If you would like independent support before or during making a complaint, you can contact:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>Patient Advice and Support Service (PASS)</strong><br>
      Free, independent advice on your rights as a patient.<br>
      <a href="https://www.cas.org.uk/pass" rel="noopener noreferrer">www.cas.org.uk/pass</a> or call 0800 917 2127
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Scottish Public Services Ombudsman (SPSO)</strong><br>
      If you are not satisfied with our response, you can escalate your complaint to the SPSO.<br>
      <a href="https://www.spso.org.uk/" rel="noopener noreferrer">www.spso.org.uk</a>
    </li>
  </ul>

</div>
